{"tid":740652,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"PS4 PRO CLUB 招後防及龍門","createTime":"2018-07-13T04:55:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-31T03:53:39.000Z","uid":34279,"like":1,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a11561c56fbef787abc0df790327082cbc7ff536","tid":740652,"uid":34279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T04:55:17.000Z","msg":"球隊為提升防守能力，希望招收以下位置：<br />\n<br />\n中堅及右閘：擁有良好位置感和判斷力，需要和防中配合防守。需有一定頭球防守能力。傳波以安全第一為首要目標。<br />\n<br />\n龍門：需要有一定經驗。<br />\n<br />\n級別：D1<br />\n隊伍陣式及打法：4231<br />\n有ANY，主要為中間地面短傳進攻，當然也會長傳，只在適當時機放直線。<br />\n<br />\n全體要求：<br />\n- 尊重隊友，不需要獨食鳩扭個人主義者，需要以球隊利益為先。<br />\n- 多走位幫波，不要只向前衝。希望球員盡量做到護球在腳。<br />\n- 不要瘋狂放直線至死位，適當時懂橫傳及後傳。<br />\n- 需要多溝通交流討論，大家一齊進步。<br />\n- 只收<span style=\"color: red;\">全職球員</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有意試腳或加入者請留TG，謝謝。"},{"pid":"406b41a95bb34f5421b0bdea2de09629abd73f54","tid":740652,"uid":34279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T06:42:44.000Z","msg":"推呀推"},{"pid":"7fcdbc29f877bf8c0040455556834004a5c20b67","tid":740652,"uid":34279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T07:21:56.000Z","msg":"Push!"},{"pid":"3e05a811a14c2bf9138a56ec9370ec4513a2050c","tid":740652,"uid":34279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T08:25:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e2d8a7d7b1e8730d147ae1b68988a201eba962b","tid":740652,"uid":34279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T11:52:19.000Z","msg":"推啊推啊推"},{"pid":"1312631ed8f4554838720712851a5b48d0883021","tid":740652,"uid":34279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T12:10:14.000Z","msg":"推啊推啊推"},{"pid":"2e01faf4a8b1efb0b2df1cfe05d4757607a7a45f","tid":740652,"uid":34279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07